        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"519727\">@Alice Ryhl</span> <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"413824\">@Gary Guo</span> </p>\n<p>If I want to submit work items containing generic data, what do I need to do?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[pin_data]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">SubmitWorker</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">run_job</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;&amp;</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Job</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">ARef</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">DmaFence</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">i32</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">jobq</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Arc</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Revocable</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">SpinLock</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">InnerJobqueue</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"cp\">#[pin]</span>\n<span class=\"w\"